description: (Updated: March 15th 2024) LoFi covers from your favorite Nintendo games like Mario, The Legend of Zelda, Pokemon, Stardew Valley, Animal Crossing, and even some tunes from Sega games and more! Featuring Mikel, Coffe Date, DJ Cutman, Closed on Sunday, Less Gravity, Mipsick, Qumu and many other
